<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Welcome to Empower Her - Verify Your Account</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #2684f0;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px;
    }

    .content {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .message {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .button {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .button a {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #2684f0;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .verification-code {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Welcome to Empower Her!</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p class="message">Hello <%= firstname %>,</p>
      <p class="message">
        Thank you for joining Empower Her! We're excited to have you as
        part of our community.
      </p>
      <p class="message">
        To complete your registration, you can either use the verification button below or enter the following
        verification
        code on the Empower Her website:
      </p>
      <div class="verification-code">
        <%= verifcationCode %>
      </div>
      <div class="button">
        <a href="<%= frontendUrl %>/verify-account?token=<%= verifcationCode %>">Verify My Account</a>
      </div>
      <p class="message">
        If you did not sign up for a Empower Her account, please disregard
        this message.
      </p>
      <p class="message">
        If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to
        contact our support team.
      </p>
      <div class="button">
        <a href="mailto:healtheworld250@gmail.com">Contact Support</a>
      </div>
      <p class="message">Warm regards,</p>
      <p class="message">The Empower Her Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>